@startuml Sequence_Contact_Support

actor User
participant "Client" as Client
participant "Contact API" as API
participant "Database" as DB
participant "Email Service" as Email

== Submit Contact Form ==
User -> Client: Fill contact form
Client -> Client: Validate form
Client -> API: POST /api/contact
API -> API: Validate data
API -> DB: Save contact message
DB --> API: Message saved
API -> Email: Send confirmation email
Email --> User: Confirmation email
API --> Client: Success response
Client --> User: Show success message

== Admin View Messages ==
User -> Client: Access admin panel
Client -> API: GET /api/admin/contact
API -> DB: Get contact messages
DB --> API: Messages list
API --> Client: Return messages
Client --> User: Display messages

== Admin Reply ==
User -> Client: Select message
Client -> API: GET /api/admin/contact/:id
API -> DB: Get message details
DB --> API: Message data
API --> Client: Return message
Client -> Client: Enter reply
Client -> API: POST /api/admin/contact/:id/reply
API -> DB: Save reply
DB --> API: Reply saved
API -> Email: Send reply email
Email --> User: Reply email
API -> DB: Mark as replied
DB --> API: Status updated
API --> Client: Success response

@enduml

